"url" : "_uml_elem_class.html#UUID-4a46c27b-6993-e326-3fcb-b4c7f8fd711a_c14152a3e7ba74bc0a86463567be68d_id_f7cc630f443059eac0a8640e000134e8", 
"breadcrumbs" : "CODESYS UML \/ 参考：编程 \/ 类图元素 \/ 元素：类 \/ 特性 ", 
